\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 What you asked for\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Bug.
\f0\b0  The "All" chip on the browse view says 
\f2\fs26 83
\f0\fs24 . The header says 
\f2\fs26 485 RECORDS
\f0\fs24 . You'd expect them to match.\

\f1\b Feature.
\f0\b0  When you expand a watch and click a dealer's "Website" button, it goes to the dealer's homepage. You want it to go straight to that specific watch on the dealer's site.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
