\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 That's a meaningful improvement: instead of hunting through their menu, you land on a page filtered to that watch.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 For watches you want a perfect direct URL:
\f0\b0  I create a file 
\f2\fs26 dealer-deep-links.json
\f0\fs24 . You (or I, when you find the URL) can drop in entries like:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs26 \cf0 \{\
  "rolex-submariner-126610ln-126610lv-126619lb": \{\
    "jtime-watch-store": "https://jtime.io/product/the-exact-page/"\
  \}\
\}\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs24 \cf0 When this entry exists, that exact URL wins over the search URL. You upgrade individual high-priority watches over time.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 Fallback:
\f0\b0  if neither a direct URL nor a search URL works for a dealer (e.g., their site doesn't have search), the button still goes to the homepage like today. So nothing gets worse.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
